ℍ𝕒𝕡𝕡𝕪 𝔹𝕚𝕣𝕥𝕙𝕕𝕒𝕪, 𝕄𝕠𝕞𝕞𝕒𝕒𝕒𝕒𝕒𝕒! 🥳🎂🍰⁣
⁣
#Impromptubaking on PH yesterday just cos I’ve all the ingredients I need for my 𝐋𝐲𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐞 𝐑𝐨𝐬𝐞 𝐂𝐚𝐤𝐞! 🌹🍰 ⁣
⁣
Presenting my fugly version of my all-time favourite cake flavour! If I remember correctly, this is my 4th whole cake I’ve baked thus far! I don’t usually bake whole cake cos it’s time consuming and my frosting skills cmi. 𝘐 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘯𝘬 𝘐’𝘮 𝘣𝘦𝘵𝘵𝘦𝘳 𝘢𝘵 𝘣𝘢𝘬𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘤𝘶𝘱𝘤𝘢𝘬𝘦𝘴~🧁⁣
⁣
PS: End product not too shabby, eh? 😉

#lycheerose #lycheerosecake #homebaker #homebaked #procrastibaking #🐷inthekitchen
Ji shi yao kai dian? Hahaha! 😍
@singaporeliciouz awww thanks babe~ 🙆🏻‍♀️💕 hope so cos I laughed at my attempt... lol
Amazing effort babe! Am sure to your mum, this is the prettiest cake ever! 😊
@crappysotong awww~ u flatter me! It’s so amateurish, I laughed when I screwed up the frosting & tried to salvage with dried rose petals and fresh lychees! Lol🤣
Wow so nice can!! Mummy must be very happy!
妈妈生日快乐! 很补的蛋糕 满满的爱 ❤️❤️❤️
@thechoyalicious thankiiiews babe! Visually still got lotsa room for improvement.. the frosting is LOL
So pretty! And lychee rose is 👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼👏🏼👏🏼👏🏼
Can share recipe babe? Have some rose buds at home thinking what to do hahaha
@elizchu yes babe! U one day after right😜
